<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Detail Donasi Pakaian - Relawan Nusantara</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-dark: #0a0f1e;
            --accent-cyan: #00d2ff;
            --card-bg: #1e293b;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--bg-dark);
            color: white;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* Header / Navbar */
        .navbar {
            padding: 20px 5%;
            background: rgba(10, 15, 30, 0.9);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }

        .back-link {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: var(--accent-cyan);
            font-weight: 600;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        /* Detail Container */
        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .hero-image {
            width: 100%;
            height: 350px;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
            border: 1px solid rgba(0, 210, 255, 0.3);
        }

        .detail-box {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            margin-top: -50px;
            position: relative;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
        }

        h1 { color: var(--accent-cyan); margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 2rem; }

        .info-list {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }

        .info-list li {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            padding: 15px 20px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .info-label { color: #94a3b8; font-size: 0.9rem; }
        .info-value { font-weight: 600; color: #fff; text-align: right; }

        .btn-submit {
            display: block;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 18px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #00f2fe, #0077ff);
            color: #0a0f1e;
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 700;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .btn-submit:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0, 242, 254, 0.4);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav class="navbar">
        <a href="/pendidikan" class="back-link">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" fill="currentColor"><path d="M15.41 16.59L10.83 12l4.58-4.59L14 6l-6 6 6 6z"></path></svg>
            Kembali
        </a>
        <div style="color: var(--accent-cyan); font-weight: bold;">Relawan Nusantara</div>
    </nav>

    <div class="container">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517677208171-0bc6725a3e60?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop" class="hero-image" alt="Donasi Pakaian">
        
        <div class="detail-box">
            <h1>Detail Program Donasi Pakaian</h1>
            <p>Salurkan pakaian layak pakaimu untuk meringankan beban saudara-saudara kita yang membutuhkan di Panti Asuhan dan daerah terdampak bencana.</p>
            
            <ul class="info-list">
                <li><span class="info-label">üìç Lokasi Penyaluran</span> <span class="info-value">Panti Asuhan / Korban Bencana</span></li>
                <li><span class="info-label">üëï Jenis Pakaian</span> <span class="info-value">Anak, Dewasa, Seragam, dll</span></li>
                <li><span class="info-label">‚ú® Kondisi</span> <span class="info-value">Layak Pakai / Baru</span></li>
                <li><span class="info-label">üöö Pengiriman</span> <span class="info-value">Drop Point / Jemput Relawan</span></li>
                <li><span class="info-label">üèÖ Reward</span> <span class="info-value">30 Koin + Lencana</span></li>
            </ul>

            <button id="donasiBtn" class="btn-submit">Donasi Sekarang</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        document.getElementById('donasiBtn').addEventListener('click', () => {
            // Ambil koin lama
            let coins = parseInt(localStorage.getItem('relawan_koin')) || 0;
            // Tambah koin baru
            coins += 30;
            localStorage.setItem('relawan_koin', coins);
            
            alert("Terima kasih pahlawan! üéâ\nDonasi kamu sedang diproses. +30 Koin ditambahkan!");
            window.location.href = "/pendidikan"; // Balik ke menu utama
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>